  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_130",
    "english": "Demon. Although an inhabitant of the Demon Realm, they can be found in the human world, in places where demonic organizations lie, such as Tokyo Kingdom or Yomihara. With physical features of a developed chin and canines, they have superhuman strength but are normal inhabitants, fearful and groveling. But to those weaker than them, they are ruthless and use crude weapons, like a metal pipe, to resist.",
